using pre-defined templates.

14
00:01:08.890 --> 00:01:13.536
The chart style section provides different
formatting options such as colors and

15
00:01:13.536 --> 00:01:14.080
styles.

16
00:01:22.911 --> 00:01:27.440
The data section allows us to manipulate
the data set that the chart is based on.

17
