20
00:01:43.570 --> 00:01:47.073
Next, on the chart tools ribbon,
we find the format tab.

21
00:01:47.073 --> 00:01:51.640
This tab provides you with a variety of
options for formatting the chart elements.

22
00:01:52.770 --> 00:01:55.710
On this tab,
we find the current selection section

23
