if we select legend, we can see that
the legend has been selected in the chart.

27
00:02:12.600 --> 00:02:15.690
The insert shapes section
provides you with the option of

28
00:02:15.690 --> 00:02:18.660
inserting an object into the worksheet.

29
00:02:18.660 --> 00:02:22.530
Such objects can be especially useful
when you're trying to call out a specific

30
